graph TB
    subgraph 数据采集层
        INC[收入数据]
        EXP[支出数据]
        HIS[历史数据]
    end

    subgraph 分析引擎
        ZBA[零基预算分析器]
        ADA[自适应调整器]
        OPT[优化器]
    end

    subgraph 预算管理
        CAT[分类预算]
        RES[小金库]
        ALT[预警系统]
    end

    subgraph 输出层
        REP[预算报告]
        REC[建议推荐]
    end

    INC --> ZBA
    EXP --> ZBA
    HIS --> ADA

    ZBA --> CAT
    ADA --> OPT
    OPT --> CAT
    OPT --> RES

    CAT --> ALT
    RES --> ALT
    ALT --> REP
    ALT --> REC
